In addition, the owner of the recreation room had to respond to the neighbours' complaints about the noise, while, according to her, the troubles were not caused by the clients of the discotheque, but by the inhabitants of the occupied house and especially the participants in the parties held there, which were more frequent and intense in recent weeks, according to the irritated neighbours of the area.
The head of the disco explained that the troubles were so great that she even reached an agreement with the owner of the building and it has been nine months since the owner "forgives" the rent.
